      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "1-tier (simple): single virtual machine",
      "pos": [
        8207,
        8246
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "In this application pattern, you deploy your SQL Server application and database to a standalone virtual machine in Azure.",
      "pos": [
        8248,
        8370
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The same virtual machine contains your client/web application, business components, data access layer, and the database server.",
      "pos": [
        8371,
        8498
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The presentation, business, and data access code are logically separated but are physically located in a single server machine.",
      "pos": [
        8499,
        8626
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Most customers start with this application pattern and then, they scale out by adding more web roles or virtual machines to their system.",
      "pos": [
