      "pos": [
        8951,
        9095
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "You want to quickly provision development and test environments for short periods of time.",
      "pos": [
        9099,
        9189
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "You want to perform stress testing for varying workload levels but at the same time you do not want to own and maintain many physical machines all the time.",
      "pos": [
        9193,
        9349
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The following diagram demonstrates a simple on-premises scenario and how you can deploy its cloud enabled solution in a single virtual machine in Azure.",
      "pos": [
        9351,
