      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "For a detailed discussion on enterprise applications, see <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>What is an Enterprise Application<ept id=\"p1\">](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/aa267045.aspx)</ept>.",
      "pos": [
        10978,
